A cyberpunk-style digital cityscape at night where towering server buildings are interconnected by glowing neon data streams in electric blue and magenta. The buildings resemble circuit boards with intricate pathways, each structure representing a different module or application plugging into a massive central hub that pulses with energy. Small holographic widgets and floating geometric shapes orbit the buildings like satellites, symbolizing add-ons and integrations. The scene has a rain-slicked street level reflecting the neon glow above, with silhouettes of people walking among the connected towers. Dense cables and fiber optic bundles weave between structures like vines in a technological jungle. The atmosphere is moody with volumetric fog catching the colored lights, creating depth and mystery. Style emphasizes sharp angular architecture, chromatic aberration effects, and a color palette dominated by deep purples, electric blues, hot pinks, and cyan accents against dark metallic surfaces.
